      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="27215818">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fq.fengqiu/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2793402-2.jpg" alt="Feng" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27215818/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27215818/" class="">第268页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fq.fengqiu/" class=" " title="Feng">Feng</a>
                (找回自己！)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27215818">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在资本主义自由经济制度中，对缺钱的恐惧、对失去工作的恐惧、对滑落到社会下层的恐惧，会鞭策人们奋发努力。我深深的感受到过这种恐惧，现在仍然感同身受。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-06-22 15:18</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">4人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在资本主义自由经济制度中，对缺钱的恐惧、对失去工作的恐惧、对滑落到社会下层的恐惧，会鞭策人们奋发努力。</q></blockquote>我深深的感受到过这种恐惧，现在仍然感同身受。
