              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33946598/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51613461/" class=" " title="苏二">苏二</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33946598">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">知识分子就像飞蛾，围绕一支蜡烛飞来飞去，为的是最终扑向火焰，带着翅膀折断的响声投入火焰之中烧成灰烬，以显示人类的光荣。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-01-08 22:09</span>
                  
                </p>
